{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"iddb0f9bcb-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s51c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"51c"},"text":"§ 51c.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" “Common stock”, “capital”, and “capital stock” defined","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The term “common stock” as used in sections 51a, 51b, 51c, and 51d ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002010"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002010"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" of this title means stock of national banking associations other than preferred stock issued under the provisions of said sections. The term “capital” as used in provisions of law relating to the capital of national banking associations shall mean the amount of unimpaired common stock plus the amount of preferred stock outstanding and unimpaired; and the term “capital stock”, as used in sections 101, 177, and 178 "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002010"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" of this title, shall mean only the amount of common stock outstanding."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"iddb0f9bcc-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1933-03-09/ch1"},"text":"Mar. 9, 1933, ch. 1","children":[],"tail":", title III, § 303, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/48/5"},"text":"48 Stat. 5","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"iddb0f9bcd-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"iddb0f9bce-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"iddb0f9bcf-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s51d"},"text":"Section 51d of this title","children":[],"tail":", referred to in text, was repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1947-06-30/ch166/tII/s206/b"},"text":"act June 30, 1947, ch. 166, title II, § 206(b)","children":[],"tail":", ("},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"o","children":[],"tail":"), "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/61/208"},"text":"61 Stat. 208","children":[],"tail":". For effect of the repeal on outstanding debentures held by banks, see note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s51b–1"},"text":"section 51b–1 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Sections 101, 177, and 178 of this title, referred to in text, were repealed by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/325/tVI/s602/f/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–325, title VI, § 602(f)(2)","children":[],"tail":", (5), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-09-23"},"text":"Sept. 23, 1994","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/108/2292"},"text":"108 Stat. 2292","children":[],"tail":", 2293."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
